headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Emerson Electric Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Emerson Electric has delivered notable outperformance relative to the broader market over the past year, and analysts continue to maintain a fairly bullish stance on its long-term growth outlook.

headline: 1 Unpopular Stock That Deserves Some Love and 2 We Brush Off
summary: When Wall Street turns bearish on a stock, it’s worth paying attention. These calls stand out because analysts rarely issue grim ratings on companies for fear their firms will lose out in other business lines such as M&A advisory.
